name: Meta terra
description: Nostalgia as reminder - the magnificence of rainforests which brought beauty to vast lands and allowed us humans to flourish. Though thriving wasn‘t enough, we had to keep pushing. With the artificial thought to need more, we also destroyed more. The lush green that we once saw was all obliterated for monetary gain. These are some of the last remaining visuals we have of its magnificence, yet act as a reminder of how fast it can be taken away from us. Let’s not to ever make that mistake again.
